review_data: Reviewed in the United States on September 15, 2021
name: ShoeGameProper
title: EXCELLENT Yogurt
review: I've tried Chobani, Stoneyfield, Fage, Nancy's.This one is my favoriteTEXTURE-smooth, creamy mouth feel.Not watery or coarseFLAVOR-It's not sweet, but it's also not tart.I'd say it's a light savory creamy dairy tasteSHELF LIFE-excellentI use it when cooking as a substitute for heavy cream, sour cream, etcI love that it's fat free and only 100 calories per generous servingNO ingredients that don't naturally constitute yogurt (it's milk and cultures.that's it)Yes it costs a little more but ifyogurt is an important part of your diet and you love it then it will satisfy you 100%

review: This is probably the mildest tasting non-fat, sugar-free yogurt. Get it if that’s what you like. I find the Chobani one a a little gamy. It also has slightly higher protein content than Chobani.
